Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念的强烈就是送达死后文的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任的强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文…文伽  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人…不太正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有碍事的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是杀人凶手啊  犯人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非法官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  我还有想要确认的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町屋翔太是你的恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有没有恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指男人的话  多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后这里会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不会变  保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  你在生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接到福音局的指示了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是‘冈德路菲’吧

Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(200,300)}{\be1}{\move(-13,13,14,13,0,500)\fs24}冈德路菲:\N{\fs21}─────────\N福音局内的上层人物{\fscx50}{\fscx100}\N

Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到居然是那种死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了  居然用死后文来做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏他还是个父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合理的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉痛的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是单纯的人心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0609
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时的你的话不是都会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持要找出收信人…绫濑明日奈的恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些男的并不是她的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩为什么要杀死她父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封死后文上写了原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那与我们的工作无关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  可是杀了自己的父亲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑她们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹美红还有些怕生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她接住了  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  快跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊把妹妹美红照顾得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她们的父亲不是一个好父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不想说过世人的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像生活很放荡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事件也不一定是不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  来了来了

