Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  明天我想休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你还以为有讨价还价的余地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  莫非有男人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能想着玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想着赚钱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的医疗费也不便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天起  让美红也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就有这样的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于模特的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这么快就有回音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙条件不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我把你们拉扯大花了我多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们  我才落得这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报点恩也是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我都不能集中精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起  睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保护了美红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及  未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说刚才来了很多警察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有尸体吗  真的假的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我们进去等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她们父亲的案子有什么进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有听明日奈提起过关于町屋翔太这名少年的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和翔太的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没跟任何人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:11:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\bord0}清洁\N\N花丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要  抹去自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0}海鸥站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往青森的SILVER ARROW
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿途停靠  大宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛冈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美红  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西想交给你

Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我说犯人啊  为什么都要往北方逃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话  绝对往南方去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的地方比较享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方  南方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹语？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是之前那样的魔术？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该传达不到的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从死后的世界寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘死后的世界’？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这是诅咒信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是町屋翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文是失去一切的人们最后一刻留下的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有接收的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒我的罪恶意识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是恐吓信？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  我没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的生或死  对我来说都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人终有一死  只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死有什么意义的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死法的不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话  周围没人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在这里扣动扳机的话  你就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去生命的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财产
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自身存在都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有所留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有所遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗…憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会用上  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是封死后文而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空  好空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  决定就坐那边的位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海鸥站坐车就都空着  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你有没有注意到刚才有个打扮奇怪的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪  好像还拿着杖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们一直在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子  看得见（幽灵）哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  少了一件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子很单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了钱啊地位之类的利益得失而犯罪的犯人并不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正可怕的是思想单纯的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致最爱的绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑  突然收到这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定吓了一大跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼了很久不知道写什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想着自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没好好想过绫濑是个什么样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此  你却相信了我的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我…杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我的  不是翔太你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经最讨厌翔太了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太总是在谈论自己的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的什么学生会会长啊  一直在学钢琴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一栋大楼里我看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏暗的屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的都是恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  翔太总在屋顶上看着无边无尽的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  说过相信翔太的火箭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想相信的不是火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  要是火箭升天了  我们也会迎来光明的明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0}明日奈&美红
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  我是野岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是再开发区域的保龄球馆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第1号到第50号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部检查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  这孩子很单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你很久了哦  明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里原来是青空游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经常带儿子来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个先不提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是私人领地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在这里会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先离开这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美红也在担心你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0}明日奈&翔太 美红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得见吗  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太是好人  肯定会上天国的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概…会下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能送到就好了  翔太的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是封有点奇怪的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这是世界上最单纯  最美丽的思念

